dct_description_sm: Ancillary map shows Rhodes and nearest Dodecanese Islands not included in main map. "Remarks" note in English has been attached to map. Map was originally accompanied by explanatory booklet "Metallogeny of Greece" (not available at Princeton University Library).
dct_publisher_sm: Athēnai : Institouton Geōlogias kai Ereunōn Hypedaphous, 1965.
